This code, except where noted, was written by Marc T. Henry de
Frahan. All questions should be directed to marchdf@umich.edu.

The Gauss quadrature functions and polynomialBasis function where in
large part inspired by the Gmsh source code (http://geuz.org/gmsh/).

The 2D version of the function pnpoly in lagrange_particles_kernels.cu
was written by W Randolph Franklin
(http://www.ecse.rpi.edu/~wrf/pmwiki/pmwiki.php).